---
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24" id="faq">
  <SectionTitle title="Frequently Asked Questions" className="mb-16" />
  
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- FAQ 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How much does it cost to build a RAG application?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">RAG application development typically starts at $5,000 for basic implementations. The cost varies based on data complexity, integration requirements, and custom features. I provide detailed quotes after understanding your specific needs during our discovery call.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What is an MCP server and do I need one?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers connect Claude Desktop to your custom data sources and tools. They're perfect if you want Claude to access your company databases, APIs, or internal systems. Starting at $2,000, they can dramatically improve your AI workflow efficiency.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">How long does it take to develop a custom AI chatbot?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">Most AI chatbots take 4-6 weeks to develop and deploy. This includes requirements gathering, data preparation, training, testing, and integration. Simple chatbots can be ready in 2-3 weeks, while complex multi-agent systems may take 8-12 weeks.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 4 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Do you work with clients outside of St. Louis?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely! While I'm based in St. Louis, Missouri, I work with clients worldwide. I've successfully delivered projects for companies across the US, Europe, and Asia. All communication is done remotely via video calls, email, and project management tools.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 5 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What makes you different from other AI developers?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">As a freelance developer, you get direct access to me throughout your projectâ€”no account managers or middlemen. I specialize in cutting-edge AI technologies like RAG systems and MCP servers, and I'm committed to learning new technologies as your project evolves. Plus, you typically save 40-60% compared to agency costs.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ 6 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
      <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 faq-button">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">What technologies do you use for full-stack development?</h3>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform duration-200 faq-arrow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </button>
      <div class="hidden px-6 pb-4 faq-content">
        <p class="text-gray-600">I primarily use React, Next.js, and Astro for frontend development, Node.js and Python (FastAPI) for backends, PostgreSQL and MongoDB for databases, and deploy on Vercel, Netlify, and Railway. For AI projects, I work with OpenAI, Anthropic, LangChain, and various vector databases.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-button');
    
    faqButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const content = this.nextElementSibling;
        const arrow = this.querySelector('.faq-arrow');
        
        if (content.classList.contains('hidden')) {
          content.classList.remove('hidden');
          arrow.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
        } else {
          content.classList.add('hidden');
          arrow.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>